  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to xcb-util-wm</title>

    <para>
      The <application>xcb-util-wm</application> package contains libraries
      which provide client and window-manager helpers for EWMH and ICCCM.
    </para>

    &lfs84_checked;

